MAGNETOMETER CALIBRATION

Heading Calibration

launch mavproxy by running this in terminal

mavproxy.py --master=/dev/ttyACM0 --baudrate 115200

magcal start | accept | cancel


start ->
magcal start

accept ->
magcal accept

needs to run for ~ 60 seconds
goal is to capture a bunch of orientations 
slowly move between all orientations such as
pitch robot downward, then pitch it upward
level out, roll it 90 degrees left, roll 90 degrees right
level out, rotate yaw 360 degrees around.

